stateDiagram-v2
  direction TB

  Starting --> Running: booted
  Running --> Snapshotting: snapshot requested
  Snapshotting --> Paused: complete
  Running --> Paused: pause or auto-pause
  Paused --> Unpausing: resume
  Unpausing --> Running: restored
  Running --> Deleting: delete requested
  Deleting --> Deleted: cleanup complete
